headline: Has Grainger (GWW) Run Too Far After Multi‑Year Share Price Surge?
summary: If you are wondering whether W.W. Grainger's share price still reflects reasonable value after a strong run over the years, you are not alone. The stock last closed at US$1,079.94, with returns of 2.1% over 7 days, 7.6% over 30 days, 7.6% year to date, 2.5% over 1 year, 64.2% over 3 years and 208.9% over 5 years, which naturally raises questions about how much is already priced in.
